Warmly received by exceptionally friendly reception staff who spoke good english, armed with ready smile to greet render assistance on directions, food, places of visits etc.	Be prepared for a detailed explanation on why you will have to pay 3 Euros per person, per night and why it has to be paid in cash only.	Service is superb, good knowleable staff with a wonderful command of the English language.	Added extras were that they provided you with a detailed map on your arrival, pointing out all the must see places, recommended resturants (although we didn't try them) and there is free internet access in the hotel with a pass code they provide you with at reception.